<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #2c2c2c
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src=" " alt=" Logo" height="60px">
            <h1><strong>ABC Company</strong></h1>
            <h1><strong>Request Rejected Notification</strong></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{borrower_name}},</p>
            <p>We regret to inform you that your <strong>{{request_type}}</strong> for the book <strong>{{title}}</strong> has been rejected. Please contact the librarian for further details.</p>
            <p><strong>Register ID:</strong> {{register_id}}</p>
            <p><strong>Borrower Name:</strong> {{borrower_name}}</p> 
            <p><strong>Book Title:</strong> {{title}}</p>
            <p><strong>Borrow Date:</strong> {{borrow_date}}</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the librarian for further details.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            2024 Library Management System. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
